name: BetterDeepSkin (BDS)
description:
Would appreciate images, feedback, requests, reviews, and of course comments in the comments. Please check out my other models if you like this one.

A Lora trained on various images with the deep_skin tag. Think it can sometimes make better breasts, though all this "better" stuff is subjective. Its more breast focused but can do other body parts. If using other Loras I would recommend messing with the weights as having both at 1 can cause too much skindentationing. (can also add texture to clothing)
weights 0.7 - 1.0
recommended tags: deep_skin, skindentation
optional tags: pov, pov_hands, breast_grab, breast_lift, ass_grab (pretty much anything involving skin indents)

optional negatives: thick, thick_thighs, fat, shiny, shiny_skin, wet (can create really thick people sometimes or shiny skin)

got worse results when using bad-hands-5.

discovered issues: Not sure if it is this model or my main checkpoint, but sometimes the skin will become a solid color - think it is my checkpoint.

Had some paizuri images in the dataset, so put paizuri in the negative if it gens it
